.container-fluid#main-banner
    .col-xs-12#main-banner-content
        %h1 Let's Create.
        %h2 Kelly McGee  /  Product Design  /  Development
        %a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lrg.buttons{href: '#about-me'} Take A Spin
.container-fluid.bucket#about-me
    .row    
        .col-sm-2
        .col-sm-8#about-me-content
            %h3 Hi There. I'm Kelly.
            %p I believe in clean, empathetic design. I'm passionate about combining these fundamentals with products and interfaces to create experiences that have the power to change our daily lives. In my mind, technology today shouldn't be defined by hashtags and shameless selfies. With beautiful code and human centered design, I hope to make meaningful future products.
            %p I'm currently a sophomore at MIT studying Mechanical Engineering and Product Design. I have over seven years of experience in Graphic Design and have worked on various tangible and intangible design projects. 
            %p Feel free to check out some of my work below.
            /= image_tag 'portrait.png', :id => 'portrait'
        .col-sm-2
/.containter-fluid.header#design-header
/    .col-sm-5
